com.amazonaws.services.stepfunctions.builder.states

Interface State

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ChoiceState, FailState, ParallelState, PassState, SucceedState, TaskState, TransitionState, WaitState

    public interface State
    Base interface for all states that can be used in a StateMachine.

    This interface should not be implemented outside the SDK.
